title: Dandelion Seed Head
description: A close-up image of a dandelion seed head against a clear blue sky. The dandelion is fully puffed out, showcasing its delicate white seeds radiating from the center, creating a fluffy appearance.

title: Pollination and Fruit Development Cycle
description: The image illustrates the cycle of pollination and fruit development. It shows a plant with roots in the soil, a flowering plant attracting bees for pollination, and the resulting cherries and seeds. The arrows indicate the flow of the process from the plant to the flower, to pollination by bees, and finally to the development of fruit and seeds.

title: Graph Representation
description: A simple line graph with a horizontal axis and a vertical axis. The graph appears to be empty, with no plotted data points or lines.

title: Chipmunk Eating Berries
description: A close-up image of a chipmunk perched on a branch, nibbling on red berries. The chipmunk has distinctive brown and black stripes along its back, and the background features soft, blurred colors that suggest a natural setting.

title: Close-up of a Green Seed Pod
description: A close-up image of a green seed pod with a spiky texture, surrounded by long green leaves. The background is a soft purple, creating a contrast that highlights the details of the seed pod.
